-- Arbuthnot Banking net interest income jumps 63 pct
-- By Aashika Jain in Bangalore
-- Thu Mar 20, 2014 03:43AM EDT
-- None



March 20 (Reuters) - Arbuthnot Banking Group Plc's <ARBB.L> full-year net interest income surged 63 percent as its retail banking division added more customers and posted higher net interest margin.

Net interest income rose to 73.1 million pounds ($121.5 million) in the year ended Dec. 31 from 44.8 million pounds a year earlier. [ID:nRST7285Ca] Net interest margin rose to 16.9 percent from 15 percent a year earlier in Secure Trust Bank <STBS.L> - Arbuthnot's retail banking division.